      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>馳騁畋獵令人心發狂，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The chariot course, and the wild hunting waste Make mad the mind; and objects rare and strange,</seg>
      </tuv>
