      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 12.6 - 老子 12.7</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>難得之貨令人行妨。是以聖人為腹不為目，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Sought for, men's conduct will to evil change. Therefore the sage seeks to satisfy (the craving of) the belly, and not the (insatiable longing of the) eyes.</seg>
      </tuv>
